HEADWORD: government-in-exile
<hw>government-in-exile</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A temporary government
moved to or formed in a foreign land by exiles who hope to rule when
their country is liberated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

